         <ol>
            <li>Log onto the MCS Windows Server as Administrator.</li>
            <li>Open Windows Explorer.</li>
            <li>Navigate to G:\Backups\Archive<fig>
                  <image href="media/image3.jpg" placement="break" align="center"/>
               </fig>
            </li>
            <li>Verify the most recent files were written last Saturday. Each backup has a set of three files.<ol>
                  <li>MCS&lt;system&gt;_Full_&lt;date and time&gt;.zip – Full backup of the Windows server.</li>
                  <li>MCS&lt;system&gt;_SQL_&lt;date and time&gt;.zip – Backup of the SQL database.</li>
                  <li>MCS&lt;system&gt;_VMS_&lt;date and time&gt;.zip – Full backup of the VMS server.</li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
